'flux2'.\n\nFalls weiterhin Fehler: ComfyUI updaten UND in den Einstellungen\n'Preview method' von 'auto' auf 'none' stellen (bekannter Klein-Bug)."],"color":"#653","bgcolor":"#432"},{"id":11,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[1278.5714285714284,692.8571428571429],"size":[480,340],"flags":{},"order":5,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"📥 Modelle & Downloads","properties":{"Node name for S&R":"MarkdownNote","cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.68"},"widgets_values":["**FLUX.2 Klein 4B base**\n\n- diffusion_models: `FLUX/flux-2-klein-base-4b.safetensors`\n- **undistilled → 20-28 Steps**, nicht 4.\n\n**Encoder-FIX:** `Qwen\\qwen_3_4b.safetensors` (Qwen3, **kein** Mistral, **kein** VL)."],"color":"#222","bgcolor":"#111"}],"links":[[1,2,0,3,0,"CLIP"],[2,3,0,4,0,"CONDITIONING"],[3,1,0,6,0,"MODEL"],[4,3,0,6,1,"CONDITIONING"],[5,4,0,6,2,"CONDITIONING"],[6,5,0,6,3,"LATENT"],[7,6,0,8,0,"LATENT"],[8,7,0,8,1,"VAE"],[9,8,0,9,0,"IMAGE"]],"groups":[],"config":{},"extra":{"ds":{"scale":0.7,"offset":[321.42857142857144,415.7142857142857]}},"version":0.4}